title: Yoke Shire - Masque of Shadows(Progressive Rock)
description:
Masque of Shadows

Released:  April 17, 1999

The multi-award winning masterpiece debut album conceived as a musical journey. Traversing sonic soundscapes with unparelled dexterity, this recording exhibits a rare breadth of originality and excellence!
